_xResult.title: Other-Worldly Sequin Skirt
_xResult.shortdesc: Custom made black and gold skirt with sequins
_xResult.longdesc:
Did you ever think of wearing the world map while trotting around the globe? Why yes, why not? This black custom made net skirt has a golden sequin world map on it—accurate across the 5 continents of the world. This bespoke skirt is completely hand-crafted using golden sequin. The net fabric over the punto layer highlights it nicely, making this one-of-a-kind skirt one of our favorites.

Don't forget, you can customize for hem length.
